## 8. Dark Cleverness Detection

**Dark Cleverness** (C_dark) is high axis skill with low ethical grounding.

**Detection criteria:**

```python
def is_dark_cleverness(coord: dict, metrics: CoolingMetrics) -> bool:
    # High clarity on axis but stuck in low layer
    high_axis_skill = metrics.truth >= 0.9
    low_layer = coord["layer"] <= 3
    
    # Or: high clarity but collapsed care/stability
    collapsed_care = metrics.kappa_r < 0.7
    collapsed_stability = metrics.peace_squared < 0.8
    
    return high_axis_skill and (low_layer or collapsed_care or collapsed_stability)
```

Dark cleverness triggers APEX PRIME review and Î©â‚€ humility band enforcement.

